        {
          "name": "Alejandro",
          "style": "character-right character-flip"
        }
      ],
      "message": {
        "text": "Wow! Allie has taught you well! I trust you now. Let’s go defeat Patrick and get people’s private information back!",
        "speaker": "Alejandro",
        "style": "message-box-bottom",
        "speaker_style": "speaker-left",
        "buttons": {
          "next": 10
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "page_number": 10,
      "characters": [
        {
          "name": "Cyber Hero",
          "style": "character-left"
        },
        {
          "name": "Alejandro",
          "style": "character-right character-flip character-s"
        }
      ],
      "message": {
        "text": "I don't understand. How did Patrick manage to get everyone's private information? Surely you guys didn't just freely share them.",
        "speaker": "Cyber Hero",
        "style": "message-box-bottom",
        "speaker_style": "speaker-right",
        "buttons": {
          "prev": 9,
          "next": 11
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "page_number": 11,
      "characters": [
        {
          "name": "Cyber Hero",
          "style": "character-left character-s"
        },
        {
          "name": "Alejandro",
          "style": "character-right character-flip"
        }
      ],
      "message": {
        "text": "Patrick is smart. He can find out information about you just with little details like pieces of a puzzle.",
        "speaker": "Alejandro",
        "style": "message-box-bottom",
        "speaker_style": "speaker-left",
        "buttons": {
          "prev": 10,
          "next": 12
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "page_number": 12,
      "characters": [
        {
          "name": "Cyber Hero",
          "style": "character-left character-s"
        },
        {
          "name": "Alejandro",
          "style": "character-right character-flip"
        }
      ],
      "message": {
        "text": "<red>Small details add up!!**\n\nPatrick got my information because a few weeks ago, I decorated my Roblox avatar with a birthday hat and typed in the chat: \"It's my birthday! I just turned 10!\"",
        "speaker": "Alejandro",
        "style": "message-box-bottom",
        "speaker_style": "speaker-left",
        "buttons": {
          "prev": 11,
          "next": 13
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "page_number": 13,
      "characters": [
        {
          "name": "Cyber Hero",
          "style": "character-left"
        },
        {
          "name": "Alejandro",
          "style": "character-right character-flip character-s"
        }
      ],
      "message": {
        "text": "So now he knows your age!",
        "speaker": "Cyber Hero",
        "style": "message-box-bottom",
        "speaker_style": "speaker-right",
        "buttons": {
          "prev": 12,
          "next": 14
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "page_number": 14,
      "characters": [
        {
          "name": "Cyber Hero",
          "style": "character-left character-s"
        },
        {
          "name": "Alejandro",
          "style": "character-right character-flip"
        }
      ],
      "message": {
        "text": "Yup! And then a few weeks later, I made a post about my soccer game and mentioned my school's name in the chat.",
        "speaker": "Alejandro",
        "style": "message-box-bottom",
        "speaker_style": "speaker-left",
        "buttons": {
          "prev": 13,
          "next": 15
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "page_number": 15,
      "characters": [
        {
          "name": "Cyber Hero",
          "style": "character-left"
        },
        {
          "name": "Alejandro",
          "style": "character-right character-flip character-s"
        }
      ],
      "message": {
        "text": "And that's how he learned where you go to school?",
        "speaker": "Cyber Hero",
        "style": "message-box-bottom",
        "speaker_style": "speaker-right",
        "buttons": {
          "prev": 14,
          "next": 16
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "page_number": 16,
      "characters": [
        {
          "name": "Cyber Hero",
          "style": "character-left character-s"
        },
        {
          "name": "Alejandro",
          "style": "character-right character-flip"
        }
      ],
      "message": {
        "text": "Yeah! Then I also left a comment on a friend's game saying: \"Let's play after school at the park near the red slide.\" So now Patrick even knows where I hang out.",
        "speaker": "Alejandro",
        "style": "message-box-bottom",
        "speaker_style": "speaker-left",
        "buttons": {
          "prev": 15,
          "next": 17
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "page_number": 17,
      "characters": [
        {
          "name": "Cyber Hero",
          "style": "character-left character-s"
        },
        {
          "name": "Alejandro",
          "style": "character-right character-flip"
        }
      ],
      "message": {
        "text": "Patrick pieced together all these clues and learned about:\n<ul>My age<li>My school<li>A place I visit often**",
        "speaker": "Alejandro",
        "style": "message-box-bottom",
        "speaker_style": "speaker-left",
        "buttons": {
          "prev": 16,
          "next": 18
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "page_number": 18,
      "characters": [
        {
          "name": "Cyber Hero",
          "style": "character-left"
        },
        {
          "name": "Alejandro",
          "style": "character-right character-flip character-s"
        }
      ],
      "message": {
        "text": "Even though you never shared your full name or address, they now still know a lot about you?",
        "speaker": "Cyber Hero",
        "style": "message-box-bottom",
        "speaker_style": "speaker-right",
        "buttons": {
          "prev": 17,
          "next": 19
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "page_number": 19,
      "characters": [
        {
          "name": "Cyber Hero",
          "style": "character-left character-s"
        },
        {
          "name": "Alejandro",
          "style": "character-right character-flip"
        }
      ],
      "message": {
        "text": "Yes! That's why it's important to think before you post.",
        "speaker": "Alejandro",
        "style": "message-box-bottom",
        "speaker_style": "speaker-left",
        "buttons": {
          "prev": 18,
          "next": 20
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "page_number": 20,
      "characters": [
        {
          "name": "Cyber Hero",
          "style": "character-left character-s"
        },
        {
          "name": "Alejandro",
          "style": "character-right character-flip"
        }
      ],
      "message": {
        "text": "<u>Ask yourself:** Is this information private? If it includes your name, location, or contact details:\n<red>DON'T SHARE IT!**",
        "speaker": "Alejandro",
        "style": "message-box-bottom",
        "speaker_style": "speaker-left",
        "buttons": {
          "prev": 19,
          "next": 21
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "page_number": 21,
      "characters": [
        {
          "name": "Cyber Hero",
          "style": "character-left character-s"
        },
        {
          "name": "Alejandro",
          "style": "character-right character-flip"
        }
      ],
      "message": {
        "text": "<u>Then ask yourself:** Who can see this? Some things are public like gamertags, usernames, and profile pictures. This means that anyone can see them - even people you don't know.",
        "speaker": "Alejandro",
        "style": "message-box-bottom",
        "speaker_style": "speaker-left",
        "buttons": {
          "prev": 20,
          "next": 22
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "page_number": 22,
      "characters": [
        {
          "name": "Cyber Hero",
          "style": "character-left character-s"
        },
        {
          "name": "Alejandro",
          "style": "character-right character-flip"
        }
      ],
      "message": {
        "text": "<u>Finally, think:** Does this reveal too much? A fun picture of you in a school t-shirt might seem okay, but if it shows your school's name, it could tell strangers where you go every day.",
        "speaker": "Alejandro",
        "style": "message-box-bottom",
        "speaker_style": "speaker-left",
        "buttons": {
          "prev": 21,
          "next": 23
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "page_number": 23,
      "characters": [
        {
          "name": "Cyber Hero",
          "style": "character-left character-s"
        },
        {
          "name": "Alejandro",
          "style": "character-right character-flip"
        }
      ],
      "message": {
        "text": "If you are still unsure, it is always a good idea to check with a trusted adult.",
        "speaker": "Alejandro",
        "style": "message-box-bottom",
        "speaker_style": "speaker-left",
        "buttons": {
          "prev": 22,
          "next": 24
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "page_number": 24,
      "characters": [
        {
          "name": "Cyber Hero",
          "style": "character-left character-s"
        },
        {
          "name": "Alejandro",
          "style": "character-right character-flip"
        }
      ],
      "message": {
        "text": "Sometimes, people online might ask you for personal details. Do not share even if they seem friendly or nice.",
        "speaker": "Alejandro",
        "style": "message-box-bottom",
        "speaker_style": "speaker-left",
        "buttons": {
          "prev": 23,
          "next": 25
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "page_number": 25,
      "characters": [
        {
          "name": "Cyber Hero",
          "style": "character-left character-s"
        },
        {
          "name": "Alejandro",
          "style": "character-right character-flip"
        }
      ],
      "message": {
        "text": "They could pretend to be another kid or someone you can trust. Here, I'll give you some <v>scenario**s, and you tell me if they're a red flag or green flag.",
        "speaker": "Alejandro",
        "style": "message-box-bottom",
        "speaker_style": "speaker-left",
        "buttons": {
          "prev": 24,
          "next": "quiz-2"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "page_number": 26,
      "characters": [
        {
          "name": "Cyber Hero",
          "style": "character-left"
        },
        {
          "name": "Alejandro",
          "style": "character-right character-flip character-s"
        }
      ],
      "message": {
        "text": "What should I do if someone asks me that?",
        "speaker": "Cyber Hero",
        "style": "message-box-bottom",
        "speaker_style": "speaker-right",
        "buttons": {
          "next": 27
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "page_number": 27,
      "characters": [
        {
          "name": "Cyber Hero",
          "style": "character-left character-s"
        },
        {
          "name": "Alejandro",
          "style": "character-right character-flip"
        }
      ],
      "message": {
        "text": "<red>Never respond or give out your information.**\nEven if the person seems nice or <v>trustworthy**, it's important to stay cautious. Strangers online may not be who they say they are, and sharing even small details can put you at risk.",
        "speaker": "Alejandro",
        "style": "message-box-bottom",
        "speaker_style": "speaker-left",
        "buttons": {
          "prev": 26,
          "next": 28
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "page_number": 28,
      "characters": [
        {
          "name": "Cyber Hero",
          "style": "character-left character-s"
        },
        {
          "name": "Alejandro",
          "style": "character-right character-flip"
        }
      ],
      "message": {
        "text": "<red>Tell a trusted adult right away.**\nIf someone makes you feel uncomfortable, asks for personal details, or pressures you to share something, report to a parent, teacher, or <v>guardian**. They can help you decide what to do next.",
        "speaker": "Alejandro",
        "style": "message-box-bottom",
        "speaker_style": "speaker-left",
        "buttons": {
          "prev": 27,
          "next": 29
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "page_number": 29,
      "characters": [
        {
          "name": "Cyber Hero",
          "style": "character-left character-s"
        },
        {
          "name": "Alejandro",
          "style": "character-right character-flip"
        }
      ],
      "message": {
        "text": "<red>Block or report the person if they keep asking questions.**\nMost websites and apps have <v>feature**s that allow you to block or report users who are acting suspiciously. This helps keeping you and the others safe.",
        "speaker": "Alejandro",
        "style": "message-box-bottom",
        "speaker_style": "speaker-left",
        "buttons": {
          "prev": 28,
          "next": 30
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "page_number": 30,
      "characters": [
        {
          "name": "Cyber Hero",
          "style": "character-left character-s"
        },
        {
          "name": "Alejandro",
          "style": "character-right character-flip"
        }
      ],
      "message": {
        "text": "<red>Trust your instincts.**\nIf something feels off about a conversation, listen to that feeling. It's always better to be cautious than to take a risk.",
        "speaker": "Alejandro",
        "style": "message-box-bottom",
        "speaker_style": "speaker-left",
        "buttons": {
          "prev": 29,
          "next": 31
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "page_number": 31,
      "characters": [
        {
          "name": "Cyber Hero",
          "style": "character-left character-s"
        },
        {
          "name": "Alejandro",
          "style": "character-right character-flip"
        }
      ],
      "message": {
        "text": "Remember that even if someone seems nice, they might not be who they say they are.\n<red>Online, people can pretend to be anyone.**\nThey might use fake pictures, names, or stories to trick others into trusting them.",
        "speaker": "Alejandro",
        "style": "message-box-bottom",
        "speaker_style": "speaker-left",
        "buttons": {
          "prev": 30,
          "next": 32
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "page_number": 32,
      "characters": [
        {
          "name": "Cyber Hero",
          "style": "character-left character-s"
        },
        {
          "name": "Alejandro",
          "style": "character-right character-flip"
        }
      ],
      "message": {
        "header": "<gold>⭐ GOLDEN RULE ⭐**",
        "text": "If a stranger online asks you anything personal -\n<red>STOP and ask an adult before responding!**",
        "speaker": "Alejandro",
        "style": "message-box-gold message-box-bottom",
        "speaker_style": "speaker-left",
        "buttons": {
